ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.seeizvr_picker.vfpwhsl.1=The Block Picker selects which blocks other items in World Builder will use.	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.seeizvr_picker.vfpwhsl.yjcqsdz=To return to one block mode:	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.seeizvr_picker.vfpwhsl.uiwhyvv=1. §7Press the §cUse Item / Place Block§7 button while §cSneaking§7 to open an additional options menu.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.seeizvr_picker.vfpwhsl.qrwzkpp=2. §7Press the §cDisable Addition Mode§7 button.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.seeizvr_picker.vfpwhsl.fanfouf=3. §7Press the §cUse Item / Place Block§7 button on any block you would like to add to your block palette.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.seeizvr_picker.vfpwhsl.qpksasl=Your block palette will now be overwritten by the newly selected block, removing any previously selected blocks.	#
