ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.seeizvr_replacer_tool.vfpwhsl.qpksasl=You can press the §cAttack / Destroy§r button on any block to pick it as the replacement block.	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.seeizvr_replacer_tool.vfpwhsl.vrqpxni=With blocks replaced lets take a look at cycling through different block states. 	#
