ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_1.message.1=New quality of life features, from a range of Clipboard Tools, to the Tool Brush Manager!	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_1.message.10=Improved tips when using items.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_1.message.11=The Selection Box is now more responsive.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_1.message.12=Open Toolbox can now be moved around in the inventory.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_1.message.13=Rearranged default toolbox layout and added new items into the inventory.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_1.message.14=Masks no longer apply to Cut item.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_1.message.15=Changed warning message when using an item with a mask applied to be more clear.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_1.message.16=Fixed a bug where your Toolbox can be stuck in the open state.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_1.message.17=Fixed Gradients not working with spaces in the name.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_1.message.2=Added new Flip item.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_1.message.3=Added new Rotate Clockwise item.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_1.message.4=Added new Rotate Anti-Clockwise item.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_1.message.5=Added new Clear Mask item.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_1.message.6=Added new Tool Brush Manager.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_1.message.7=Added a Reset Toolbox button to the Handbook.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_1.message.8=Added improved How to guide.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_1.message.9=Added Oreville Studios contact details in the Handbook.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_1.title=1.1 Update	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_2.message.1=Performance improvements, compatibility with Custom Blocks, and bug fixes!	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_2.message.2=Custom blocks added by other Add-Ons can now be picked using the Block Picker.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_2.message.3="Include Air" and "Include Entity" settings are now persistent after resetting inventory.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_2.message.4=Fixed entities created using World Builder not getting despawned by Undo and Redo items.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_2.message.5=Fixed a memory leak, performance no longer decreases the longer a world is open.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_2.title=1.2 Update	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.1=Customisable Toolboxes, and many new Tools to put in them! World Builder 1.3 also includes several quality of life fixes to make your experience even better!	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.10=You can now add more Structures into your Structure Brushes.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.11=All tools are now droppable from your inventory.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.12=Brush Outlines can now be toggled off separately to the Selection Box outline.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.13=Tools can now be shared and edited in multiplayer.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.14=Slightly optimized the Erosion Brush.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.15=Adaptive segment count for the sphere wireframe - working with small brushes should be less obstructive to your view.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.16=Fixed an issue with the Toolbox randomly resetting itself under certain circumstances.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.17=Fixed an issue with your inventory randomly clearing itself under certain circumstances.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.18=Fixed structure-placed chests from spilling out their items when undone.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.19=Fixed other miscellaneous issues.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.2=Added new Replace Tool: Change blocks to other blocks.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.3=Added new Ruler Tool: Find the center of your Selection, divide a Selection into equal segments, and get more Selection information.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.4=Added new Distant Selection Wand: Make Selections from very far away.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.5=Added new Ellipsoid Draw Shape.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.6=Added new Torus Draw Shape.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.7=Added new Dome Draw Shape.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.8=Added new Toolbox customisation: You can now customize the layout of your Toolbox, and add up to 8 new Toolboxes.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.message.9=Added a Sound volume slider in the World Builder Settings.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_3.title=1.3 Update	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_4_1.message.1=Fixing bugs from the 1.4 Update!	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_4_1.message.2=Fixed an issue that could cause World Builder's tools to stop working under certain circumstances.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_4_1.message.3=Fixed an issue with structure brushes not saving properly when reloading your world.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_4_1.message.4=Fixed an issue with fluid replacement.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_4_1.message.5=Fixed drawing tools erroring at height limit.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_4_1.title=1.4.1 Update	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_4.message.1=The all new Permissions System gives more control to Realm Operators, and World Hosts. We've also improved some of our most used Tools and Brushes!	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_4.message.10=Reduced the wireframe size of the sphere brush for smaller brushes to make them less intrusive and improve visibility.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_4.message.11=Fixed an issue where using the replace tool on blocks with a shared family such as andesite or granite, would instead turn to stone.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_4.message.2=Added a Permission system, giving Operators more control over the tools that can be used. (More info in the How to Guide!)	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_4.message.3=Added a Whitelist system for granting and revoking players access to World Builder. (More info in the How to Guide!)	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_4.message.4=Added a new "Changelog" tab into the World Builder Handbook for viewing past update features.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_4.message.5=The Cylinder Draw Shape can now be drawn horizontally.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_4.message.6=Improved the Flip Tool: Flip your builds upside down.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_4.message.7=Improved the Command Tool: Execute up to 8 commands from a single Tool.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_4.message.8=Improved the Structure Brush: Apply a height offset to choose where your structures are pasted from.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_4.message.9=The "Give Handbook on World Join" setting now applies to all players when toggled on, or off.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_4.title=1.4 Update	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5_1.message.1=Performance improvements and bug fixes, after the 1.5 Update!	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5_1.message.2=Improved performance degrading over time with long play sessions.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5_1.message.3=Fixed an issue causing tools to stop working when updating from 1.4.1 to 1.5 in a pre-existing world.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5_1.message.4=Fixed an issue with Selection Fill Masks.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5_1.message.5=Fixed an issue with Structure Brushes.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5_1.message.6=Some of your previously created custom tools may have broken in this update. We will do our best to ensure it doesn't happen in future updates!	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5_1.title=1.5.1 Update	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.1=A new Run Command Tool, new Starter Tools and Brushes, and even more control over Draw Shape Tools!	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.10=§7- §cmove <distance>§7: Moves a selection by a specified amount, optionally including air or entities.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.11=§7- §ccopy §7/ §cpaste§7: Copies and pastes the current selection, with flags to ignore air or limit by a mask.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.12=§7- §cstack [count: int]§7: Duplicates a selection in a specific direction.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.13=§7- §cexpand <amount>§7: Increases the size of the selection box. 	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.14=§7- §ccontract <amount>§7: Reduces the size of the selection box.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.15=§7- §cshift <amount>§7: Moves the selection box in a specific direction.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.16=§7- §cinset <amount>§7: Shrinks the selection box inward from all directions.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.17=§7- §coutset <amount>§7: Expands the selection box outward in all directions.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.18=§7- §cdeselect §7/ §csel§7: Clears the current selection. 	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.19=§7- §ccut§7: Removes the selection and saves it to the clipboard.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.2=§fNew Default Selection Wand	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.20=§7- §ccut§7: Removes the selection and saves it to the clipboard.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.21=§7- §crotate [angle]§7: Rotates the clipboard around a specified axis.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.22=§7- §cundo §7/ §credo§7: Reverts or reapplies up to 64 previous actions.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.23=§7- §cline <block>§7: Draws a line between two points in the selection. 	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.24=§7- §csphere <block>§7: Creates a spherical shape, with optional hollow and directional settings.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.25=§7- §ccylinder <block>§7: Creates a cylindrical shape, with options for height and hollowness.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.26=§7- §ctorus <block>§7: Generates a torus with specified radii and hollowness.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.27=§7- §cpyramid <block>§7: Builds a pyramid structure.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.28=§7- §cblockid§7: Identifies the block the player is looking at. 	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.29=§7- §ccancel [job:int]§7: Cancels ongoing operations.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.3=§7- Select blocks or points in space, even mid-air, for both Position 1 and Position 2. 	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.30=§7- §chelp <command>§7: Displays help for a specific command.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.31=§7- §cjumpto §7/ §cj§7: Teleports to the target location the player is looking at.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.32=§7- §cup <height>§7: Moves the player up and places a block beneath them.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.33=§7- §cunstuck§7: Moves the player to the nearest open space. 	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.34=§7- Error-handling hints for unsupported commands and invalid blocks, with suggestions to check the handbook.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.35=§7- Added hints for invalid commands, suggesting valid alternatives.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.36=§7- Messages for unrecognized blocks with suggestions to check the handbook.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.37=§fNew Tools	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.38=§f- Added Advanced Rotation Tool: §7Rotate your clipboard to off-axis XYZ specific angles, great for organic and advanced builds.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.39=§f- Added Count Command: §7Counts blocks in a selection matching a mask. 	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.4=§7- Interact with selection faces using the new Wand to expand or contract your Selection as needed.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.40=§f- Added Starter Brushes: §7Pre-configured brushes for common actions.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.41=§7- Block Cycler	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.42=§7- Block Replacer	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.43=§7- Smite Tool	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.44=§7- Night Vision Toggle 	#
