ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.46=§7- River Brush	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.47=§7- Lava Brush	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.48=§7- Lily Pad Brush	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.49=§7- Foliage Brush 	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.5=§7- Sneak-use the Wand to toggle between new and Classic Selection Modes.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.50=§7- Flower Brush	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.51=§7- Path Brush	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.52=§7- Ice Brush	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.53=§fShape Tool 	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.54=§7- Added more control over shape generation.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.55=§7- Define the hollow structure of shapes.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.56=§7- Choose how hollow walls are generated.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.57=§7- Set shapes to draw from the center, or off a surface.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.58=§7- Added crouch-menu settings for Cylinder, Dome, Pyramid, and Torus shapes to toggle between horizontal and vertical orientations. 	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.59=§fMiscellaneous	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.6=§fNew Run Command Tool	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.60=§7- Changed "Submit" to "Save Changes" for better clarity.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.61=§7- Added Delete All Gradients Button.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.62=§7- Improved behind the scenes logic and database system for better performance.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.7=§7Execute actions with text-based commands. See the How-to Guide for details.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.8=§7- §cset <block>§7: Sets all blocks in a selection to the specified block. 	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.message.9=§7- §creplace <mask>§7: Replaces specific blocks in a selection with another block.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.selection.message.1=The Selection Wand has been upgraded to hopefully be more user friendly and powerful.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.selection.message.2=Instead of hitting a block and interacting with another to make a selection, you use it like the draw tools. Use it on a block and then on any point in space; even mid-air.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.selection.message.3=After creating a selection you can also use the wand to drag its faces around. Expanding and contracting it as you please.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.selection.title=Selection Wand Upgraded!	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_5.title=1.5 Update	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.1=Massive selection edits, an all new Trays system for better organisation, fancy 3D items and a variety of new and powerful Tools - World Builder 1.6 packs a tons of quality of life improvements, bug fixes and new features to make building even better!	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.10=Added new Scale tool. You can now increase the size of your builds!	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.11=Added new Drain Run Command tool, for draining Water or Lava pools at your location. The command §cdrain 10§7 will drain water in a radius of 10.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.12=Added new Recursive Fill Run Command tool, useful for filling in holes. The command §cfill stone 5 3§7 will Fill stone in a radius of 5, and depth of 3.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.13=Added new Rock Starter Tool.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.14=Added new Bush Starter Tool.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.15=Added new Starter Layouts for Toolboxes and Trays. Including layouts for Basics, Terrain Tools and Technical Blocks, or create your own.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.16=Added new Selection Expansion Tool.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.17=Added the option to delay commands with the Command Tool. For example, you could set §cgamemode spectator§7, and then §cgamemode creative§7 with a 2 second delay, as a quick way to pass through walls.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.18=Added the ability to rename Tools.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.19=Added confirmation when you are deleting a Toolbox, Layout, or Tool.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.2=Added new Infinite Selection feature. World Builder can now perform copy, paste, and all other operations at a massive scale. (§oNote: Although you can now use infinite sized selection, we recommend keeping your operations under 10,000,000 blocks - experiment with what works best for you, but use with caution!§r§7)	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.20=Made Delete buttons red for extra clarity.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.21=Improved the Smiter Tool.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.22=Added pos1 and pos2 commands to set your selection box positions with the Run Command Tool.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.23=Selection boxes are now persistent when you log out of the world and return.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.24=Renamed all instances of "pattern" to "palette" for better clarity.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.25=Improved language on the Whitelist page.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.26=Improved the How to Guide text and fixed some incorrect grammar and mistakes.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.27=Added "Next Steps" button to the How to Guide to make it easier to navigate, page by page.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.28=When using the Block Picker or Mask Picker, the name of the block now displays in your action bar, rather than just saying "Block".	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.29=The Give Item button chat text will now display the name of the item when given.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.3=Added a new "Load Chunks for Jobs" setting, which will let you know when you are about to do large edits. You can change this to Always to skip the confirmation, or Never to disable this feature.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.30=Changed default Stack Amount from 2 to 1 when using the Selection Stack tool.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.31=Changed default iterations in Smooth.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.32=Added sneak menus to Toolboxes and Trays.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.33=Improved the Whitelist and Permissions screens. Users with the tag of §cworldbuilder.op§7 will now be able to manage the Whitelist directly from the "Player Permissions" tab in the World Builder Handbook. A Remove Offline Users button will now appear when you have offline users in your world who previously had World Builder permisson, which allows you to revoke offline players World Builder access.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.34=Put Tools into Categories in the Creative Menu.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.35=Added Clear Selection button in the Sneak menu for Selection Wands.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.36=Prevented Navigation Wand from occasionally making you stuck inside of blocks.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.37=Changed "Ok" to "Confirm" in confirmation dialogues.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.38=Renamed Reset Toolbox button to Delete Toolbox so that it is more clear.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.39=Fixed an issue causing Structure Void blocks occasionally being left behind when doing edits.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.4=Added 8 new Trays, a new type of storage which can be used inside of your Toolbox.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.40=Fixed an issue occasionally causing air blocks to be copied even if the Copy Air Settings is turned off.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.41=Fixed an issue causing the Add-On to break if custom blocks have a hyphen in their ID.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.42=Fixed an error that can occasionally break the Add-On. (TypeError: cannot read property 'owner' of undefined.)	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.43=Fixed an issue that could let you have duplicate brush names when creating them via the Run Command tool.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.44=Fixed slightly inaccurate line tool preview ghost.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.45=Using the Replacer wand without blocks now works.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.46=Fixed an issue with the cut Run Command.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.47=Fixed an issue where the Navigation Wand could sometimes teleport you inside of blocks.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.5=Added new 3D Items for all World Builder items.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.6=Added new Cone Draw Shape.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.7=Added new Curve Draw Shape, with the option to set thickness.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.8=Added new Smooth Selection tool for smoothing large amounts of terrain more easily.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.message.9=Added new Blob Brush, great for building more natural looking rocks or terrain.	#
ui.oreville_wb:handbook.changelog_1_6.title=1.6 Update	#
