ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.sdtkvvx_brush.vfpwhsl.vrqpxni=Your Cylinder Brush will now be in your inventory	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.sdtkvvx_brush.vfpwhsl.xclccmg=To use the Cylinder Brush:	#
