ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.sdtkvvx_brush.vfpwhsl.vjnannn=Press the §cUse Item / Place Block§r button while §cSneaking§r to adjust the brushes settings.	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.sdtkvvx_brush.vfpwhsl.fqzcsma=Want to use your own builds to quickly paint villages together? Lets take a look at the Structure Brush.	#
