ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.sdtkvvx_brush.vfpwhsl.5=3. §7Press the §cCylinder Brush§7 button.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.sdtkvvx_brush.vfpwhsl.6=4. §7Move the §cSize§7 slider to the size you would like your cylinder to be.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.sdtkvvx_brush.vfpwhsl.7=5. §7Move the §cHeight§7 slider to the height you would like your cylinder to be.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.sdtkvvx_brush.vfpwhsl.8=6. §7Use the §cHollow§7 button to toggle between a solid or hollow cylinder.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.sdtkvvx_brush.vfpwhsl.9=7. §7Press the §cSave Changes§7 button.§r	#
