ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.fill_tool.vfpwhsl.fpdlmcv=Next we will look at the Command Tool	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.fill_tool.vfpwhsl.2=To create a fill tool:	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.fill_tool.vfpwhsl.3=1. §7Press the §cUse Item / Place Block§7 button while holding the Tool Brush Manager to open an options menu.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.fill_tool.vfpwhsl.4=2. §7Press the §c+ New Tool§7 button.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.fill_tool.vfpwhsl.5=3. §7Press the §cFill Tool§7 button.§r	#
