ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.lghzamp.vfpwhsl.3=1. §7Create a selection using the Selection Wand.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.lghzamp.vfpwhsl.4=2. §7Make a copy of your selection using either the Copy or Cut item.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.lghzamp.vfpwhsl.5=3. §7While holding the Flip item. Face the direction you would like your clipboard to be flipped across.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.lghzamp.vfpwhsl.6=4. §7Press the §cUse Item / Place Block§7 button while holding the Flip item.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.lghzamp.vfpwhsl.7=Your clipboard will now be flipped across the direction you are facing. To see the effect of this item, paste your clipboard using the Paste item.	#
