ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.cwyutyy.vfpwhsl.1=The Rotate Clockwise and Anticlockwise items, rotate your clipboard by 90degrees in either direction.	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.cwyutyy.vfpwhsl.yjcqsdz=1. §7Create a selection using the Selection Wand.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.cwyutyy.vfpwhsl.uiwhyvv=2. §7Make a copy of your selection using either the Copy or Cut item.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.cwyutyy.vfpwhsl.qrwzkpp=3. §7Press the §cUse Item / Place Block§7 button whilst holding the advanced rotation item. Alternatively Press the §cSneak/Flydown §7and §cUse Item / Place Block §7buttons while holding the Rotate Clockwise or Rotate Anticlockwise item.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.cwyutyy.vfpwhsl.fanfouf=4. §7You will bring up the advanced Rotation menu allowing you to change the degree of rotation across the X, Y and Z axis'.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.cwyutyy.vfpwhsl.qpksasl=5. §7Once you are happy press "Save Changes".§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.cwyutyy.vfpwhsl.vrqpxni=Your clipboard will now be rotated by your set parameters. To see the effect of this item, paste your clipboard using the Paste item.	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.cwyutyy.vfpwhsl.xclccmg=§o§7Note: A preview of your clipboard will appear while holding the Rotate items. The position of this preview is set by where you were standing when you made the copy.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.cwyutyy.vfpwhsl.hqtfelu=Rotate not what your looking for? Next we'll look at Flip!	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.cwyutyy.vfpwhsl.2=To use the Rotate items:	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.cwyutyy.vfpwhsl.3=1. §7Create a selection using the Selection Wand.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.cwyutyy.vfpwhsl.4=2. §7Make a copy of your selection using either the Copy or Cut item.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.cwyutyy.vfpwhsl.5=3. §7Press the §cUse Item / Place Block§7 button while holding the Rotate Clockwise or Rotate Anticlockwise item.§r	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.cwyutyy.vfpwhsl.6=Your clipboard will now be rotated by 90degrees. To see the effect of this item, paste your clipboard using the Paste item.	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.cwyutyy.vfpwhsl.7=Advanced Rotation	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.cwyutyy.vfpwhsl.8=The Advanced Rotation gives you more control over your clipboard.	#
