ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.ljaqbfb.vfpwhsl.4=A settings menu will be opened with the following options:	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.ljaqbfb.vfpwhsl.5=- Sound Volume:§7 Controls the volume of World Builders sound effects.§r 	#
ui.oreville_wb:gbpmshn.ljaqbfb.vfpwhsl.6=- Load Chunks for Jobs:§7 Select between Always, Never or Request Permission for large builds and edits to chunk load. This process will lock player movement and camera for the duration of the job.§r	#
